      • testCycleDetection

        public void testCycleDetection()
        Creates the following graph and verifies that the cycle is found. 
                 A
       /   \
     B       C <----|
   /   \   /        |
 D       E          |
   \   /            |
     F --------------
        Note that there is a circular dependency from F -> C -> E -> F.
